// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Secrets template — COMMITTED to the repo (safe; contains no real key).
//
// Setup:
//   1. cp Secrets.example.xcconfig Secrets.xcconfig   (Secrets.xcconfig is gitignored)
//   2. Get a Gemini API key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
//   3. Paste it after the "=" below in your Secrets.xcconfig
//
// The key flows: Secrets.xcconfig -> Info.plist ($(GEMINI_API_KEY)) -> read at runtime.
// It is never hard-coded in Swift source. For production, move this behind a
// server-side proxy so the key never ships in the app binary (see README).
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
GEMINI_API_KEY =
